    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Jo-seph was a-mazed____ to___ see__ that which tran-scend----ed na---ture’s bounds,___ for with-out seed, thou,_____ O___ Maid,__ didst__ both____ con-ceive_____ and bear a__ Child. And he re-mem------bered the blos--som---ing rod___ of Aa-----ron,__ the dew___ up--on the fleece,____ and the__ un-burn--ing________ bush which___ was__ not con-sumed,____ though it__ was all___ a--------flame. Thus, thy pro-tec---tor____ and be-trothed_____ cried, as he bare wit-ness__ be-fore___ the______ priests: A Vir-----gin__ bear---eth, and af-----ter child--------birth, still re-main-eth__ a Vir-----gin."
    }
